TITLE: Adding CORS Policy in ConfigureServices Method
DESCRIPTION: C# code for adding a CORS policy to enable cross-origin requests to the Reporting REST Service. This adds a policy that allows any origin, method, and header.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/embedding-reports/host-the-report-engine-remotely/asp.net-core-web-api-implementation/host-reports-service-in-.net-5.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
services.AddCors(corsOption => corsOption.AddPolicy(
	"ReportingRestPolicy",
	corsBuilder =>
	{
		corsBuilder.AllowAnyOrigin()
			.AllowAnyMethod()
			.AllowAnyHeader();
	}
));
```

