TITLE: Handling ItemDataBinding Event in C# for Telerik Reporting
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to handle the ItemDataBinding event in a section of a Telerik report. It retrieves a reference to a specific TextBox in the section and modifies its value based on data source column values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/embedding-reports/program-the-report-definition/report-events/using-section-events.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
private void Detail_ItemDataBinding(object sender, EventArgs e) {
    // Get reference to the section object
    var section = (Telerik.Reporting.Processing.ReportSection)sender;
    // Find specific TextBox in the section
    var textBox = section.Items.Find("textBox1", true).FirstOrDefault() as Telerik.Reporting.Processing.TextBox;
    // Alter the TextBox value based on the data source
    textBox.Value = section.DataObject.GetColumnValue("ColumnName");
}
```

