TITLE: Binding ObjectDataSource to BusinessObject in C#
DESCRIPTION: This C# code snippet demonstrates creating a custom business object, configuring an ObjectDataSource, and previewing a report using the Windows Forms Report Viewer. The business object includes methods returning various data types and supports method parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/designing-reports/connecting-to-data/data-source-components/objectdatasource-component/bind-to-a-businessobject.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

