TITLE: Creating ConfigurationHelper in C# for ASP.NET Core
DESCRIPTION: Defines a static ConfigurationHelper class with a ResolveConfiguration method to load the application configuration from appsettings.json.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/knowledge-base/adding-reporting-net-core-mvc.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Hosting;
using Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration;

namespace WebApplication1
{
	static class ConfigurationHelper
	{
		public static IConfiguration ResolveConfiguration(IWebHostEnvironment environment)
		{
			var reportingConfigFileName = System.IO.Path.Combine(environment.ContentRootPath, "appsettings.json");
			return new ConfigurationBuilder()
				.AddJsonFile(reportingConfigFileName, true)
				.Build();
		}
	}
}
```

