TITLE: Implementing Custom Parameter Editor Functions in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code defines the matchFunction and createEditorFunction for the custom parameter editor. The matchFunction determines if the editor should be used for a given parameter, while createEditorFunction creates the CheckBoxGroup widget and handles value changes.
