TITLE: Creating Custom Parameter Editor for DateTime in HTML5 MVC Report Viewer
DESCRIPTION: This script sets up a custom parameter editor for a DateTime parameter in the HTML5 MVC Report Viewer. It replaces the default editor with a custom date picker input formatted to a specified date format. Dependencies include jQuery and Kendo UI components. Key parameter: parameter determines if the editor applies to DateTime types.
