TITLE: Implementing Custom Cache in VB.NET
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows the implementation of a custom cache in VB.NET for Telerik Reporting. The `MyCache` class implements the `ICache` interface, providing custom logic for storing and retrieving cached data. It requires the `Telerik.Reporting.Cache.Interfaces` namespace.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/embedding-reports/cache-management/configuring-custom-cache-provider.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: VB.NET
CODE:
```
Imports System
Imports System.Collections
Imports Telerik.Reporting.Cache.Interfaces

Namespace MyNameSpace
    Public Class MyCache
        Implements ICache
        Private hashtable As New Hashtable()

        Public Property Item(key As String) As Object Implements ICache.Item
            Get
                Return hashtable(key)
            End Get
            Set(value As Object)
                hashtable(key) = value
            End Set
        End Property

        Public Sub Remove(key As String) Implements ICache.Remove
            hashtable.Remove(key)
        End Sub

        Public Sub Clear() Implements ICache.Clear
            hashtable.Clear()
        End Sub

        Public Sub Dispose() Implements IDisposable.Dispose
            ' Clean up any resources being used.
        End Sub
    End Class
End Namespace
```

