TITLE: Converting SVG to Bitmap using UserFunction in C#
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines a UserFunction that converts an SVG file to a Bitmap. It uses the Svg NuGet package to open and render the SVG document. The function takes a URL as input and returns a 120x120 pixel Bitmap.
