TITLE: Unpackaging TRDP Report Definition in Telerik Reporting with C#
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to unpackage a predefined .TRDP report definition using the ReportPackager class in C#. It reads a .TRDP file and extracts the report definition, returning a Report object.  This allows the report to be loaded and used within the application.
