TITLE: Selecting Product Details - SQL Query
DESCRIPTION: This SQL query fetches product name, ID, and number along with category ID from the AdventureWorks database. It joins the Product, ProductSubcategory, and ProductCategory tables to obtain all necessary details.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/knowledge-base/create-master-detail-report-using-subreport-item.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: SQL
CODE:
```
SELECT
    P.Name,ProductID,ProductNumber,PC.ProductCategoryID
FROM
    Production.Product P,
    Production.ProductSubcategory PS,
    Production.ProductCategory PC
WHERE
    P.ProductSubcategoryID=PS.ProductSubcategoryID
    AND PS.ProductCategoryID=PC.ProductCategoryID
```

