TITLE: Creating Custom Classes with C# for Telerik Report Designer
DESCRIPTION: Example code that creates a Car class and a Cars collection class in C# that can be used as custom objects for Telerik Reporting. The Cars class is a List<Car> that initializes with sample car data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/knowledge-base/how-to-use-external-assemblies-with-custom-clr-objects-in-the-report-designer.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: C#
