LANGUAGE: Expression
CODE:
```
= Ifs(Exec("table1", Max(Len(Fields.data))) <= 13, "0.2in",
		Exec("table1", Max(Len(Fields.data))) <= 26, "0.4in",
		Exec("table1", Max(Len(Fields.data))) <= 39, "0.6in", "0.8in")
```

