TITLE: Downloading Exported PDF Report
DESCRIPTION: Downloads the exported PDF report document to a temporary file and opens it using the default PDF viewer
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/knowledge-base/export-a-report-from-telerik-report-server-via-dot-net-client.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
static void DownloadPDF(string path, string documentID, bool asAttachment)
{
    var queryString = "";
    if (asAttachment)
    {
        queryString += "?content-disposition=attachment";
    }

    string fileName = "test1.pdf";
    string folderName = System.IO.Path.GetTempPath();
    string filePath = System.IO.Path.Combine(folderName, fileName);
    using (System.Net.WebClient myWebClient = new System.Net.WebClient())
    {
        myWebClient.DownloadFile(path + documentID + queryString, filePath);
    }

    System.Diagnostics.Process.Start(filePath);
}
```

