TITLE: Query Detail Data - Product Information
DESCRIPTION: SQL query to retrieve product details with category relationships for the detail table section. Joins multiple product-related tables to get comprehensive product information.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/knowledge-base/create-master-detail-report-using-table.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: SQL
CODE:
```
SELECT
		P.Name,ProductID,ProductNumber,PC.ProductCategoryID
	FROM
		Production.Product P,
		Production.ProductSubcategory PS,
		Production.ProductCategory PC
	WHERE
		P.ProductSubcategoryID=PS.ProductSubcategoryID
		AND PS.ProductCategoryID=PC.ProductCategoryID
```

