TITLE: Accessing Section Children in VB.NET for Telerik Reporting
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to access all children of a detail section in a Telerik report using VB.NET and set a background color for each child element. It emphasizes using the appropriate interfaces for accessing children.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/embedding-reports/program-the-report-definition/report-events/using-section-events.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: VB.NET
CODE:
```
Private Sub Detail_ItemDataBound(sender As Object, e As EventArgs)
    ' Get reference to the section object
    Dim section As Telerik.Reporting.Processing.ReportSection = CType(sender, Telerik.Reporting.Processing.ReportSection)
    ' Loop through all children and set BackgroundColor
    For Each child In section.Children
        child.Style.BackgroundColor = Color.LightGray
    Next
End Sub
```

