TITLE: Setting Kendo DatePicker Culture with JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code demonstrates setting the Kendo widget culture to Spanish (Paraguay) using the `kendo.culture` method before initializing the report viewer. Key functionality includes setting the service URL and report source for the Telerik Report Viewer. Dependencies include prior inclusion of Kendo UI and required scripts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telerik/reporting-docs.git/blob/master/knowledge-base/how-to-change-the-culture-of-the-datepicker-in-html5-mvc-report-viewer.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
<script type="text/javascript">
    kendo.culture("es-PY");

    $("#reportViewer1")
        .telerik_ReportViewer({
            serviceUrl: "https://demos.telerik.com/reporting/api/reports/",
            reportSource: {
                report: "Employee Sales Summary.trdx",
            }
        });
</script>
```

